  <brief_title>A Long Term, Safety Study of Apricitabine in HIV-infected Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open Label Long Term Safety Extension Study of Apricitabine in Treatment-experienced HIV-1 Infected Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
